28
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:34,340
SPEAKER_13: Why don't you have a go?
Show them what it takes.

105
00:11:00,720 --> 00:11:03,879
SPEAKER_13: Why don't you go home?
There'll be other times.

106
00:11:04,220 --> 00:11:06,450
SPEAKER_13: Your wife is right here.

107
00:11:07,620 --> 00:11:10,559
SPEAKER_13: What's with you?
Can't take "no" for an answer?

108
00:11:11,799 --> 00:11:15,360
SPEAKER_13: You want to make me lose face? Go away!

164
00:17:32,680 --> 00:17:37,269
SPEAKER_13: No, Fugui's signature is on each one.

165
00:17:39,019 --> 00:17:42,950
SPEAKER_13: Long'er, is our Xu family home...

166
00:17:43,049 --> 00:17:46,650
SPEAKER_13: enough to settle Fugui's debt?

167
00:17:47,319 --> 00:17:49,160
SPEAKER_13: Good.

168
00:17:51,130 --> 00:17:55,829
SPEAKER_13: A gambling debt's a debt,
and debts must be paid.

175
00:18:33,940 --> 00:18:36,740
SPEAKER_13: I thought I'd live my final days here.

187
00:19:55,250 --> 00:19:58,549
SPEAKER_13: I'll look after her for a few days?

188
00:19:58,690 --> 00:20:00,920
SPEAKER_13: Until you're set up elsewhere.

189
00:20:05,759 --> 00:20:07,349
SPEAKER_13: Want me to help you?

245
00:25:21,210 --> 00:25:22,910
SPEAKER_13: They are fabulous.

672
01:18:49,890 --> 01:18:51,609
SPEAKER_13: It's me, Chunsheng.

727
01:23:15,250 --> 01:23:17,619
SPEAKER_13: Don't you see what they are?

728
01:23:19,220 --> 01:23:21,590
SPEAKER_13: Emperors, scholars and beauties.

729
01:23:21,760 --> 01:23:23,550
SPEAKER_13: Classic feudal types.

747
01:25:24,310 --> 01:25:26,649
SPEAKER_13: I've found just the man for her.

748
01:25:29,119 --> 01:25:30,909
SPEAKER_13: His name is Wan Erxi.

750
01:25:35,890 --> 01:25:38,920
SPEAKER_13: He is the leader of the factory's Red Guards.

753
01:25:45,229 --> 01:25:47,329
SPEAKER_13: He's also got a handicap...

754
01:25:47,800 --> 01:25:49,170
SPEAKER_13: a lame leg.

759
01:26:01,020 --> 01:26:03,310
SPEAKER_13: No, it was an accident at work.

760
01:26:04,189 --> 01:26:05,979
SPEAKER_13: He gets compensation.

761
01:26:08,890 --> 01:26:12,489
SPEAKER_13: Shall we invite him over?
Fengxia can check him out.

762
01:26:17,130 --> 01:26:20,029
SPEAKER_13: Does she mind us playing matchmaker?

763
01:26:21,300 --> 01:26:24,899
SPEAKER_13: She's not opposed,
she does fret about leaving us.

780
01:28:19,590 --> 01:28:20,920
SPEAKER_13: I'll be going.

1063
01:52:02,239 --> 01:52:03,399
SPEAKER_13: I mean, older ones.

1072
01:52:40,550 --> 01:52:41,710
SPEAKER_13: Let me think.

1088
01:54:15,010 --> 01:54:17,029
SPEAKER_13: Dr. Wang, don't be afraid.

